      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be shown to be sufficiently representative of the intended use conditions at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under flow rates and pressure heads spanning the CPB operating envelope. The validation domain adequately covers the conditions under which worst-case hemolysis identification is required."
    },
    {
