      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of test sample variability is not required at MRL 2; Gradation 1 is acceptable.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark data were collected using bovine blood with documented hematocrit range. Formal statistical analysis of inter-sample variability is not required at MRL 2."
