    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required Gradation levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. Note: this submission conforms to the Minimal profile and does not include a structured Context of Use object; intended use scope is described narratively in the package description.",
